				<aside>
				<h2>So remember...</h2>
					<ol id="orderedlist">
						<li>Don't become too enveloped in your own head. We all tend to overthink.</li>
						<li>Take some breaks and enjoy what else life has to offer. We can't work 24/7.</li>
						<li>Create for yourself, not anyone else. It's important to enjoy your own creativity.</li>
						<li>Mistakes are not failures. They happen once in a while, and that's okay.</li>
						<li>Keep on creating. Never stop doing what you love.</li>
					</ol>
